          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1602249233020-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1602249233020-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble your burger, sandwich the <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>breaded chicken</strong>, <strong>bacon jam</strong> and a dollop of<strong> mayo</strong> inside the <strong>warmed brioche halves</strong> – this is your <strong>American-style chicken burger with bacon jam</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> sweet potato fries </strong>and a <strong>buttery sweetcorn cobette</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
